            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464983953574-0892a716854b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Learning Illustration" class="img-fluid hero-illustration mt-4 ms-lg-4 d-none d-lg-inline-block" style="max-width: 320px;">
